OL,3,C'He absolutely loved life' say parents
OL,4,Cof student killed by a drug driver
OL,6,FITV Border's Kieran MacFadzean went to
OL,7,Fmeet Oliver's parents.
OL,9,FOliver Pryde was on his way back to
OL,10,Fhis student accommodation after
OL,11,Fwatching England play in the Euro 2020
OL,12,Ffinal when he was hit by 33-year-old
OL,13,FAdam Smith in Huddersfield.
OL,15,FWest Yorkshire Police said Smith had
OL,16,Fconsumed nearly twice the legal limit
OL,17,Fof drugs when he ploughed into Mr
OL,18,FPryde, from Flimby in west Cumbria.
