OL,3,C'He absolutely loved life' say parents
OL,4,Cof student killed by a drug driver
OL,6,FHe was found guilty of causing death
OL,7,Fby careless driving after a trial at
OL,8,FLeeds Crown Court.
OL,10,FHis parents say they are "relieved
OL,11,Fthat he's off the street and relieved
OL,12,Fwith a 10 year sentence".
OL,14,FHis mother, Stacey Pryde said: "Lots
OL,15,Fof people think a life for a life, but
OL,16,Fgiven the guidelines, 10 years was a
OL,17,Fgood sentence for us."
