OL,3,C'He absolutely loved life' say parents
OL,4,Cof student killed by a drug driver
OL,6,FHis father Cameron Pryde added: "There
OL,7,Fare a lot of things the kids find hard
OL,8,Fto do, there are a lot of things I
OL,9,Ffind hard to do, that I just can't do
OL,10,Fany more.
OL,12,FDescribing their eldest son, Mrs Pryde
OL,13,Fsaid: "He was quirky and had a very
OL,14,Fdry sense of humour, he was football
OL,15,Fdaft.
OL,17,F"He was friendly and would do anything
OL,18,Ffor anybody, he was kind hearted.
OL,20,F"He absolutely loved life.
