OL,3,C'He absolutely loved life' say parents
OL,4,Cof student killed by a drug driver
OL,6,F"People would say you only live once,
OL,7,FOliver would say you only die once,
OL,8,Fyou live every single day."
OL,10,FOliver had ambitions of being a
OL,11,Fteacher after finding a passion for
OL,12,Fhelping people during his time at
OL,13,FNetherhall School, his mum said: "He
OL,14,Fwanted to be a teacher - he wanted to
OL,15,Finspire the next generation like he'd
OL,16,Fbeen inspired".
OL,18,FRemembering the last time she saw her
OL,19,Fson, Mrs Pryde said: "Last time I saw
OL,20,Fhim was my 40th birthday.
