OL,3,C'He absolutely loved life' say parents
OL,4,Cof student killed by a drug driver
OL,6,F"People kept saying, 'you're getting
OL,7,Fold', and I said age is a privilege
OL,8,Fand it was denied to many - I didn't
OL,9,Fknow it was going to smack me in the
OL,10,Fface 17 days later"
OL,12,F"I didn't even hug him the morning he
OL,13,Fleft because he didn't like being
OL,14,Ftouched and I knew he was coming home
OL,15,Ffor Summer in three weeks."
